 &lt;p&gt;Participants can select sessions based on their interests and availability, ensuring a personalized learning experience.&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="col-md-6 columnBlockLayout" style="flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 20px;"&gt;
